{
  "stem": "13258.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From there, they were taken on trains, which-- the kind which Solzhenitsyn describes in his where each fellow sits in a little, separate cell so that he can communicate with the others.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In wagons like this, they were taking-- and they were taking to camps which-- in Siberia, we were not surrounded by a fence.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a forest, and we went to work without a guard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, he got into a real gulag-type camp, where the people went to work with guards in the quarries-- in stone quarries, among others.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That particular fellow, who had been the chief of that restaurant chain for which I worked in Tarnopol for a while, he had military boots-- high boots, new ones-- and a military belt.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He exchanged that with the commander of the jail for being assigned to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what saved him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Many of them didn't survive there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was-- that was tough work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a lot of in-fighting going on, because the guards were stealing and some of the-- similar, like, in the concentration camps, some of the foremen or kind of capos-- they didn't call them, in Russia, that-- were involved in trades and stealing and some of oppression of some of the other guys.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had worked in job assignments, and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some of the people really suffered.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a lot of people died in those [? stone quarries. ?]",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good decision that you and your father didn't go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good decision that we didn't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Good decision that we didn't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't-- want them to separate, because they knew families will have a hard time to escape.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you are a single person, you are taking a risk, much easier.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
